sections.text: plan, defined.Network plan shall mean health insurance coverage offered by a health carrier under which the financing and delivery of medical care including items and services paid for as medical care are provided, in whole or in part, through a defined set of providers under contract with the health carrier.SourceLaws 1997, LB 862, ยง 41.
